text: Renée Brasseur (27 August 1902 - 26 June 1929) was a Luxembourgian swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1929 deaths Category:Luxembourgian female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Luxembourg Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
